# labor/state/  -- JSONL state for the orchestrator
#
# orc creates four files here on first run:
#   postings.jsonl      -- every job posting drafted via `orc post`
#   applications.jsonl  -- every applicant surfaced via `orc inbox`
#   work.jsonl          -- every completed work item via `orc score`
#   payments.jsonl      -- payment audit trail (alongside work rows)
#
# These files are committed empty as a known starting state for the
# 4-channel Phase-1 test. John can grep / wc them at any time; no DB.
